parameters: No good! It's too dangerous to sail any further!
Karin-san, I can see an island over there!

Could it be a deserted island!? If we keep going like this,
the ship will sink! Let's take refuge on that island for
now!

Hmm...! That island gives off a bad vibe... My divination
with the Bagua tells me it's an ominous sign.

Even so, if we continue north, we'll be nothing but seaweed!
Let's take emergency refuge on that deserted island until
the storm passes! Is that alright with you, Karin-san?

Yes! Please, Kisanosuke-san! Steer the ship towards the
deserted island!

Karin and the others directed the ship towards the deserted
island!
